<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Muon! muonna kim! Khawvel gitloh thim ah,
 Isu thisan in lunggil a muon sak.

[V2]
 2. Muon! Muonna kim! sep khawknan ei phak tieng,
 Isu deih bang bawl chawlhdam na ahi.

[V3]
 3. Muon! Muonna kim! lungkham kinawk mahleh,
 Isu angsung bel leng hai pai ina.

[V4]
 4. Muon! Muonna kim! I ngaihte gamlat tieng,
 Isu vennan amau tawh I bit ui.

[V5]
 5. Muon! Muonna kim! tunung ding I he puou,
 Isu I heu, Lalchutphah chunga chu.

[V6]
 6. Muon! Muonna kim! thihna hung tung mahleh,
 Isu thihna leh a hatna'n A zo.
 7. Ahun tai lei dogal bei pai tana,
 Isun van muonna kim chang di'n ei sam.</lyrics>
<title>PEACE! PERFECT PEACE!</title>
<hymn_number>328</hymn_number>
</song>